title: New: Palm Honey – Palace
body:
Here’s some woozy, Tame Impala indebted psych-pop for you, from Reading quartet **Palm Honey**.

With the summer months (hopefuly) just round the corner, and festival season kicking into gear in the coming weeks, it may be a little early for these guys to make an impact this year, but this is definitely the sort of sound and ambition that takes you to those sort of stages. Check out _Palace_ below.
